001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.types;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonSubTypes;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo;
005import java.lang.String;
006
007/**
008 * (https://docs.commercetools.com/api/projects/productTypes#attributetype)[https://docs.commercetools.com/api/projects/productTypes#attributetype]
009 */
010@JsonTypeInfo(
011    use = JsonTypeInfo.Id.NAME,
012    include = JsonTypeInfo.As.PROPERTY,
013    property = "__typename"
014)
015@JsonSubTypes({
016    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = BooleanAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "BooleanAttributeDefinitionType"),
017    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = DateAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "DateAttributeDefinitionType"),
018    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = DateTimeAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "DateTimeAttributeDefinitionType"),
019    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = EnumAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "EnumAttributeDefinitionType"),
020    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = LocalizableEnumAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "LocalizableEnumAttributeDefinitionType"),
021    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = LocalizableTextAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "LocalizableTextAttributeDefinitionType"),
022    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = MoneyAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "MoneyAttributeDefinitionType"),
023    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = NestedAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "NestedAttributeDefinitionType"),
024    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = NumberAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "NumberAttributeDefinitionType"),
025    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ReferenceAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "ReferenceAttributeDefinitionType"),
026    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = SetAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "SetAttributeDefinitionType"),
027    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = TextAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "TextAttributeDefinitionType"),
028    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = TimeAttributeDefinitionType.class, name = "TimeAttributeDefinitionType")
029})
030public interface AttributeDefinitionType {
031  String getName();
032
033  void setName(String name);
034}
